I '''Anderson Hays Cooper''' (mibait Junio 3, 1967) metung yang Americanung periodista, talasulat libru, ampong personalidad king telebisyon. Ya ing manimunang [[News presenter#News anchors|anchor]] ning palageng balitang [[CNN]] a ''[[Anderson Cooper 360°]]''. Keraklan, mibubulalag ya ing programang ''live'' manibat king studio king New York Lakanbalen; nanupata, bubulalag yang ''live'' i Cooper king lugal nung nu malilyari para kareng istoryang [[breaking news]]. Manibat Setiembre 2011 anggang Mayo 2013, migsilbi yang host ning sarili nang pang-aldong pang-aldong ''talk show'', ing ''[[Anderson Live]]''.<ref name="Kenneally">{{cite web|last=Kenneally|first=Tim|url=http://tv.yahoo.com/news/anderson-coopers-talk-show-end-second-season-172600420.html|title=Anderson Cooper's talk show to end after second season|publisher=''The Wrap'' via Yahoo.com|date=October 29, 2012|accessdate=October 30, 2012}}</ref>

